The following shader files in this directory contain code adapted from
Dylearn's 3D Pixel Art Grass Demo:

  - clouds.gdshaderinc  (cloud shadow system)
  - mst_grass.gdshader   (wind, displacement, toon lighting portions)

Source: https://github.com/DylearnDev/Dylearn-3D-Pixel-Art-Grass-Demo

The original project uses a dual-license structure:

  - Code (scripts & shaders): MIT License
  - Art assets: CC BY 4.0

The code portions adapted here fall under the MIT License, reproduced below.

